original: Lindberg, Stig Martin, tandläkare, Alingsås, f. 12/7/04 i Kristinehamn av disp. Carl Fredrik L. o. Hilma Söderström. G. 34 m. May Wicknertz. Barn: Barbro f. 35, Margareta 36, Anders o. Stig 40. — Stud:ex. i Malmö 25, tandhkand. 28, tandl. 30. Vik. i Lindesberg 30, prakt, i Alingsås sed. 31. Medl. av Frimurarorden o. Göt. förb.
translated: Lindberg, Stig Martin, dentist, Alingsås, b. 12/7/04 in Kristinehamn to unmarried parents Carl Fredrik L. and Hilma Söderström. Married in 1934 to May Wicknertz. Children: Barbro b. 1935, Margareta b. 1936, Anders and Stig b. 1940. — Graduated from Malmö School 1925, dental studies completed in 1928, became a dentist in 1930. Worked temporarily in Lindesberg in 1930, started practicing in Alingsås in 1931. Member of the Freemasonry Order and the Götaland Association.
